casebody.data:
Coy Gilbert JACOB, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
Janet S. DARROW, as Manager of Guilford Drive, LLC, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-2184 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. January 14, 2019

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The parties' joint stipulation for dismissal filed January 3, 2019, is treated as a notice of voluntary dismissal and is granted. This appeal is dismissed. The parties' motions for fees are denied as moot.
